# 🌐 API & HTTP Methods — Quick Notes

## What is an API?
An **API (Application Programming Interface)** lets two apps talk to each other.
Think of it as a **waiter** — you (client) order food, waiter (API) carries it to the kitchen (server) and brings back the response.

---

## What is HTTP?
**HTTP (HyperText Transfer Protocol)** is the language used to communicate over the web.
Every request has:
- **URL** → where to send the request
- **Method** → what action to do (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE)
- **Headers** → extra info (like auth token)
- **Body** → data you send (for POST/PUT)

---

## HTTP Methods

### ✅ GET — Read / Fetch data
> "Give me the data"

```http
GET https://api.example.com/users/1
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Sinchana",
  "email": "sinchana@example.com"
}
```
- No body in request
- Safe & idempotent (calling it 10 times = same result)

---

### ➕ POST — Create new data
> "Here's new data, save it"

```http
POST https://api.example.com/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sinchana",
  "email": "sinchana@example.com"
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "id": 5,
  "message": "User created successfully"
}
```
- Has a **body**
- Not idempotent (calling it 10 times = 10 new records)

---

### ✏️ PUT — Update existing data
> "Replace this with new data"

```http
PUT https://api.example.com/users/5
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sinchana SV",
  "email": "sv@example.com"
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "id": 5,
  "message": "User updated successfully"
}
```
- Replaces the **entire** resource
- Idempotent (same result if called multiple times)

---

### 🗑️ DELETE — Remove data
> "Delete this record"

```http
DELETE https://api.example.com/users/5
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "message": "User deleted"
}
```

---

## Quick Comparison Table

| Method | Action   | Has Body? | Idempotent? | Use Case              |
|--------|----------|-----------|-------------|----------------------|
| GET    | Read     | ❌ No     | ✅ Yes      | Fetch user, list data |
| POST   | Create   | ✅ Yes    | ❌ No       | Register, submit form |
| PUT    | Update   | ✅ Yes    | ✅ Yes      | Edit profile          |
| DELETE | Remove   | ❌ No     | ✅ Yes      | Delete account        |

