## Python Example (using `requests`)

```python
import requests

BASE = "https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com"

# GET
res = requests.get(f"{BASE}/posts/1")
print(res.json())

# POST
res = requests.post(f"{BASE}/posts", json={"title": "Hello", "body": "World"})
print(res.status_code)  # 201

# PUT
res = requests.put(f"{BASE}/posts/1", json={"title": "Updated"})
print(res.json())

# DELETE
res = requests.delete(f"{BASE}/posts/1")
print(res.status_code)  # 200
```

> 💡 `jsonplaceholder.typicode.com` is a free fake API — great for practicing!

