## Key Terms

| Term        | Meaning                                      |
|-------------|----------------------------------------------|
| Endpoint    | A specific URL path (`/users`, `/posts/1`)   |
| Request     | What the client sends to the server          |
| Response    | What the server sends back                   |
| JSON        | Most common data format for APIs             |
| REST API    | API that follows HTTP rules (most common)    |
| Auth Token  | Key sent in headers to prove identity        |






